cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI 

This paper deals with the development of a control system for biped robots, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also involves optimization and control theory, which could fall under systems and control (cs.SY). The use of computer vision techniques for balance control could also place this paper under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper involves machine learning techniques for real-time control, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
